DiDi is focused on developing Level 4 autonomous driving technology to enhance transportation safety and efficiency. The Foundation Model Team is dedicated to building large-scale foundation models for multi-agent behavior prediction and autonomous vehicle planning, utilizing extensive driving data to train robust deep learning systems.
